                "invention-title": [
                    "Hydrogen production, storage and charging system and configuration method",
                    "一种制储充氢系统及配置方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The embodiment of the invention provides a hydrogen production, storage and charging system and a configuration method, particularly relates to a hydrogen production, storage and charging system taking electrolytic hydrogen production, solid alloy or organic matter liquid hydrogen storage materials as hydrogen storage and release materials, and provides the configuration method of the hydrogen production, storage and charging system based on hydrogen use requirements and material characteristics. Through cooperation of the hydrogen production unit, the hydrogen storage unit and the hydrogen desorption unit, the total investment is the lowest under the condition of meeting the hydrogen demand, and the investment cost is saved; meanwhile, the influence of the temperature and the pressure on the working characteristics and the total investment of the hydrogen storage and release materials is considered, and a selection scheme of the optimal working condition is given, so that the hydrogen storage materials and the hydrogen release materials in the system are in a dynamic cycle of hydrogen absorption, storage and hydrogen release, and all hydrogen storage modules and all hydrogen release modules are fully utilized."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明实施例提出了一种制储充氢系统及配置方法，以电解制氢、固体合金或有机物液体储氢材料作为储放氢材料的制储充氢系统，提供了基于用氢需求和材料特性的制储充氢系统的配置方法，通过制氢单元、储氢单元、放氢单元之间的协同配合，实现在满足用氢需求条件下的总投资最低，节约投资成本；且同时考虑了温度和压力对储放氢材料工作特性和总投资的影响，给出了最佳工况的选择方案，使得系统内的储氢材料和放氢材料处于吸氢、存储和放氢的动态循环内，并使得所有储氢模块和放氢模块均获得充分利用。"
                }
            ]
